# Symposium — AI the Rust Way

Use the bundled script to invoke Symposium commands. The script finds or installs the binary automatically.

**Important:** The script path is relative to this skill's directory. Use the full path:

    ${CLAUDE_SKILL_DIR}/scripts/symposium.sh cargo check
    ${CLAUDE_SKILL_DIR}/scripts/symposium.sh cargo test --all
    ${CLAUDE_SKILL_DIR}/scripts/symposium.sh cargo clippy

